This paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as it focuses on context modeling for robots. It also involves machine learning techniques such as deep learning and Boltzmann Machines, which are commonly used in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computer Vision (cs.CV), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes an incremental model, which is a common topic in Neural Networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
